      "created": 1777378388,
      "updated": 1777378388
    },
    {
      "id": "69f0a26400000000007d65d8",
      "text": "from [幕末の三舟]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777377893,
      "updated": 1777377978
    },
    {
      "id": "69f0a26400000000007d65da",
      "text": "山岡鉄舟（剣の達人）知らんのかい[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777377893,
      "updated": 1777377893
    },
    {
      "id": "69f0a26400000000007d65db",
      "text": "\t[suto3.icon]さんの深い知見が大いにご披露されるときが楽しみですね！☺️[Anonymous.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777377893,
      "updated": 1777377893
    },
    {
      "id": "69f0a26400000000007d65dc",
      "text": "\t　マジで知らないの？（困惑している）[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777377893,
      "updated": 1777377893
    },
    {
      "id": "69f0a26400000000007d65dd",
      "text": "　　知らない[seibe.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777377893,
      "updated": 1777377893
    },
    {
      "id": "69f0a4ec00000000007d65e8",
      "text": "　　 以下、知らない➔困惑が[無限再帰]していきそう [suto3.icon]",
